## DARK THEME PALETTE

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| Background | `#0a0a0a` | Page background, layout root |
| Sidebar | `#111111` | Sidebar, cards, dropdowns |
| Elevated | `#1a1a1a` | Dropdown menus, modals |
| Border | `rgba(255,255,255,0.06)` | Subtle dividers |
| Primary | `#7C3AED` | Buttons, active states |
| Text primary | `#fafafa` | Headings |
| Text muted | `#71717a` | Secondary text |

---

## GENERAL CODING RULES

1. **TypeScript**: no `any` types. Define proper interfaces in `types/index.ts`.
2. **No Tailwind for structure**: use inline styles for layout-critical properties.
3. **No `router.push` for auth**: use `window.location.href` after sign-in/out.
4. **Supabase client**: always `createBrowserClient` in client components.
5. **Every `DropdownMenuLabel` must be inside `DropdownMenuGroup`** (Base UI rule).
6. **New pages**: match existing dark theme — `bg-[#111111]` cards, `border-white/[0.06]` borders.
7. **Run `npm run build` after every feature** and fix all errors before committing.
8. **Commit message**: `git add . && git commit -m "feature: description"`.

---

## MODULE STRUCTURE

```
app/
  (auth)/          — login, signup, forgot-password (no layout wrapper)
  (dashboard)/     — all protected routes, uses DashboardLayout
  demo/            — public demo (no auth), uses DemoLayout
  onboarding/      — post-signup flow (step-1, step-2, step-3)
components/
  layout/          — sidebar, topbar (CRITICAL — see rules above)
  analytics/       — add-account-drawer, video-detail-drawer
  campaigns/       — (campaign components)
  payments/        — invite-creator-drawer, process-payout-modal, create-rule-drawer
  competitors/     — add-competitor-drawer
  demo/            — demo-banner, signup-gate-modal
  ui/              — shadcn/base-ui component wrappers
lib/
  supabase.ts      — exports createBrowserClient instance (NOT createClient)
  auth.ts          — getCurrentUser(), isAuthenticated(), signOut()
  platform.tsx     — PLATFORM_CONFIG with bgColor/fgColor (real CSS values)
  analytics-data.ts, campaigns-data.ts, payments-data.ts, trends-data.ts,
  competitors-data.ts — Supabase data layer per module
middleware.ts      — protects all dashboard routes, reads session from cookies
```
